## Critical Success Factors

- **Desirability signal must be strong** (at least 3 tests passed)
- **Retention thesis must be clear** (habit/frequency driver)
- **Monetization wedge must be defined** (first paid moment, expansion revenue, value metric)
- **Moat map must be complete** (2+ types with implementation plan)
- **Lifecycle state machine must be designed** (before coding)
- **Churn-prevention triggers must be defined** (before coding)

## Notes

- This playbook ensures defensibility and monetization are validated before engineering
- It prevents building features that have demand but no retention or monetization path
- It forces explicit moat strategy before building
- It ensures lifecycle loops are designed before coding
- It prevents "free audience, no business" scenarios
